parameters: "Hmm, the entire cave is quite eerie, isn't it..."

"(The change in the ecosystem of the monsters must have
happened recently. That means it's a fast-breeding parasitic
type.)"

"(This type of tentacle monster stays in one place and
indeed breeds quickly but...)"

"(However, if they just keep multiplying carelessly, the
control over the tentacles will be lost, so they're not
simply splitting. There must be one main tentacle they're
all connected to.)"

"(If that's the case, defeating the boss should solve
everything.)"
"Dyuhuhu!! This looks like it'll be tough to defeat."

"(If Maroges had some understanding of the situation here
beforehand...)"

"(And on top of that, he mistakenly thought that the request
wouldn't be complete until all the tentacles were
defeated...)"

"(Then he must be optimistic that it's impossible to defeat
all the tentacles here.)"

"(So if I defeat the boss without him noticing, the request
will be completed and the moment the brainwashing is lifted,
I can capture Maroges.)"
